// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
//  GAP-09 — multi-file schema (transitional sediment file)
//
//  Empty as of step 2: every model and enum has been relocated to
//  its domain file. This file is retained as a marker so contributors
//  immediately see that the schema is split, and so future
//  not-yet-categorised models have a clear staging location.
//
//  See:
//    base.prisma          — generator + datasource (the only file
//                            that ever owns those blocks)
//    enums.prisma         — every shared enum
//    auth.prisma          — Tenant / User / Membership / Session / SSO / Billing
//    compliance.prisma    — Control / Risk / Evidence / Framework / Policy /
//                            Asset / Issue / Finding / Task (work-item) / Snapshot
//    vendor.prisma        — Vendor + assessment graph
//    audit.prisma         — Audit / AuditCycle / AuditPack / AuditorAccess /
//                            AuditLog
//    automation.prisma    — AutomationRule / Execution / Notification /
//                            Integration / SyncMapping
//
//  Migration discipline: the split was purely organisational — no
//  field, relation, index, default, or @@map changed during the
//  move. `prisma migrate diff` against the prior committed state
//  emits "This is an empty migration."
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
